{
  "stem": "27340.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he was obviously too tolerant or too friendly towards the Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that didn't fit in quite with the Nazi regime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that must have been I suppose in 1934, '35.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was aware of the Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was aware of Nazi organizations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We saw them parading up and down the streets very often.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'd been warned by my parents to keep clear of them, not to interfere, not to get involved in anything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But on occasions I was beaten up by gangs of Hitler Youth boys who were more or less my age, perhaps a year old, perhaps a year younger.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They usually operated and marauded in gangs of three or four.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was difficult as one against four to hold one's own.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But quite clearly, I did my best and defended myself, [LAUGHS] and as you can see, I'm still here to tell the tale.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After I finished the so-called Volksschule, which was the sort of junior school, I then graduated to a grammar school, a gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And since Breslau had a fairly large Jewish community of about 21 or 22,000 all together, they had two Jewish schools.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One was attached or was next to the synagogue that I mentioned to you early on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the other one was a-- a-- a-- a-- grammar school to which I went.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was at that grammar school that whenever we came out of school, almost invariably there were hordes of Hitler Youth boys waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they set upon us and doffled us up, as it were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So that-- by that time, we were very, very conscious of anti-Semitism, yes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were not allowed to go to sports places other than those that had in fact been accredited specifically for Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
